author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Sascha Rodekamp "jQuery Drag'n'Drop for myPortal" (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-3891) - OFBIZ-3891
A patch which make the myPortal Drag'n'Drop Functions work with jQuery. Tested in FF3, IE 7 / 8. The jQuery implementation works much better under IE than the Prototype one.
